  "item": [
    {
      "name": "üîê Autenticaci√≥n",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Obtener JWT Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"api_client_id\": {{api_client_id}}\n}\n\nO si prefieres usar la API Key:\n{\n  \"api_key\": \"cf748e82fecc6eb55e362fa623c6a4addf72f26cb3179c3f6d665f2730091e5c\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{clients_url}}/api/v1/authenticate",
              "host": ["{{clients_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "authenticate"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene un JWT token usando:\n- api_client_id: 1 (ID del cliente)\n- O api_key: <key> (API Key mostrada en los seeds)\n\nCuando ejecutas ./bin/start.sh ves:\n‚úÖ API Client created: Default API Client\n   API Key: cf748e82fecc6eb55e362fa623c6a4addf72f26cb3179c3f6d665f2730091e5c\n\nPuedes usar CUALQUIERA de estos dos formatos:\n\n1. Con api_client_id:\n   {\"api_client_id\": 1}\n\n2. Con api_key:\n   {\"api_key\": \"cf748e82fecc6eb55e362fa623c6a4addf72f26cb3179c3f6d665f2730091e5c\"}\n\nAmbos generar√°n el mismo JWT token"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (jsonData.token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', jsonData.token);",
                  "        console.log('‚úÖ Token guardado:', jsonData.token);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
